{"title":"打旱井","authors":["韩起祥"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"打旱井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩起祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡叫三遍东方亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小俩口要打旱井走出庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你扛镢头我拿锨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土筐麻绳都带全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥掏土妹妹吊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一唱一和还哼着夯歌调。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥挑土真像金刚钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹呀！你吊土赛过电风扇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥的心情比钢铁硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕那雪厚三尺土地冻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹的热情像热火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能烧化冰雪流成河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流成河，灌旱井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不用旱天求雨把天等。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱井肚大口口小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨水下来走不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这旱井，八尺宽来丈二深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你算算能蓄雨水多少斤？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常言说：海水不能用斗量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看看，遍山的旱井一行行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一行行、一串串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像珍珠断了线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今后，无旱涝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的生活就来到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨黄河，过长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取每亩千斤粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载“街头说唱”  第二期）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}